name: Large clean private room close to downtown
description:
Located adjacent to the Longwood Medical area and close to downtown, my house is a 5 minute walk from the Orange and Green Line (E) subways. Also within walking distance are a supermarket, ZIP car rental, restaurants, as well as museums, concert halls, Fenway Park, and multiple college campuses. The Hynes and Boston Convention Centers are easily accessible by public transportation. Free parking, access to garden. Ideal location for both, tourists and business travelers. License # STR400257

The space
My house sits on a cliff with downtown views, yet is surrounded by a beautiful garden where guest can relax. This is quite unique for downtown Boston.

License number
STR-400257
